{
  "stem": "17845.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 101.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived to Leninsk, I think it was summer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we wanted to see what-- how we're going to survive there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, you know, my father didn't want to go to work in his profession, because they were saying whoever works in Russia has to steal, otherwise he can't survive.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he-- he wasn't ready to do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for a while, we didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then I can't remember distinctly when it happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to sell something on the black market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My-- my uncle used to go out and sell this and that, or whatever they could to survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then somebody said that he-- that perhaps he could try to do-- to manufacture soap.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember exactly how he came about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then one day I remember, the-- early in the morning, the Russian babushkas used to come to our place, and bringing oil and bringing caustic soda.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to Dad, what are you going to do with that?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, I'm going to make soap.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I says, so how do you know how to make soap?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somebody told me how to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm going to try it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so the factory started in our house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they used to come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to steal, actually, that caustic soda and oil from the factory they used to work, the Russian women.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to come at 4 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had the balloons of oil and soda attached to their legs, and used the big-- how do you call it-- the skirts, so it covered them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nobody-- somehow they-- either they knew the people who watched the factories that they're doing it or not, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
